<i>noun</i>: 서광 [서ː광] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>서광 [서ː광]</dt><br>
<dd>1. gleam</dd><br>
<dd>해가 떠올라 날이 밝아올 때 비치는 새벽의 빛.</dd><br>
<dd>Light shining when the sun is going up and day is breaking.</dd><br>
<dd>2. gleam; good sign</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 일이 잘 풀리거나 좋아질 듯한 희망의 징조.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A sign of hope that things will go well or get better.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>